# This repo IS ~/.claude. Claude Code also writes its own internal state here
# (session history, shell snapshots, caches, etc.) that we never want tracked.
#
# Rather than trying to list every internal file Claude Code might create —
# which changes across versions — this ignores everything by default and
# explicitly un-ignores only what we've actually authored. Anything new
# Claude Code adds in the future stays untracked automatically.

/*
!.gitignore
!README.md
!CLAUDE.md
!settings.json
!install.ps1

!agents/
!agents/**
!commands/
!commands/**
!skills/
!skills/**

!project-template/
!project-template/**
!scripts/
!scripts/**
